data.title: Obituary for Diane M. (Frampton) McClead
data.meta_description: Diane McClead | January 23, 2024 & Newville, PA | Diane M. McClead, 58, of Carlisle...
data.meta_site_name: Obituary for Diane M. (Frampton)  McClead | Egger Funeral Home, Inc.
data.text:
Diane M. McClead, 58, of Carlisle passed away Tuesday January 23, 2024 in her home.

She was born November 22, 1965 in Buffalo, New York, the only child James and Helen Frampton.

Mrs. McClead had been a Teachers Aide for many years in the Big Spring School District, and most recently had worked for Chartwells at Mt. Holly Springs Elementary School. Miss Diane was loved by the students at both schools, and will be greatly missed.

Diane is survived by her husband Paul A. McClead, one daughter Ashley McClead, one son Paul A. McClead Jr., his girlfriend Kristen Becker, her children Blake and Colton, and two grandchildren Haley, and LeAnn.

A viewing will be held Monday January 29, 2024 from 4 to 8 PM in the Egger Funeral Home Inc, 15 W. Big Spring Ave. Newville.
